# ECLIPSE — ML Research Block Diagrams

> No project files were modified. All diagrams are derived from plans, code, and reports.

---

## 1. Overall System Architecture

```mermaid
flowchart TD
    classDef user fill:#4A90D9,stroke:#2C5F8A,color:#fff
    classDef frontend fill:#7B68EE,stroke:#4B3FA0,color:#fff
    classDef backend fill:#2ECC71,stroke:#1A7A44,color:#fff
    classDef model fill:#E67E22,stroke:#A04A00,color:#fff
    classDef store fill:#95A5A6,stroke:#5D7275,color:#fff
    classDef response fill:#E74C3C,stroke:#922B21,color:#fff

    U([User]):::user
    FE[React Native Frontend]:::frontend
    BE[Flask Backend API]:::backend
    EM[Emotion Service]:::model
    FU[Fusion Engine]:::model
    RG["Response Generator GPT-2"]:::response
    DS[(Feature Vector Store)]:::store

    U -->|Types slash Speaks slash Shows face| FE
    FE -->|POST /chat + typing_metadata| BE
    FE -->|POST /voice + audio| BE
    FE -->|POST /face + frame| BE
    BE --> EM
    EM --> FU
    FU --> RG
    RG -->|Clean adaptive response| BE
    BE -->|JSON reply| FE
    FE -->|Displays response| U
    EM -->|Feature vectors only| DS
```

