## 2. Full Multimodal Emotion Pipeline

```mermaid
flowchart LR
    classDef input fill:#3498DB,stroke:#1A5276,color:#fff
    classDef model fill:#E67E22,stroke:#784212,color:#fff
    classDef fusion fill:#27AE60,stroke:#145A32,color:#fff
    classDef output fill:#E74C3C,stroke:#922B21,color:#fff

    subgraph INPUTS["Inputs"]
        T[Text Message]:::input
        KS[Keystroke Metadata]:::input
        AU[Audio WAV]:::input
        FR[Camera Frame]:::input
    end

    subgraph MODELS["ML Models"]
        BERT["BERT-base-uncased\nText Emotion 7 classes"]:::model
        HS["Hesitation Score\nWeighted Formula"]:::model
        LBRS["Librosa Features\nRule-based Speech Model"]:::model
        CNN["OpenCV + CNN\nFER 7 classes"]:::model
    end

    subgraph FUSION["Fusion Engine"]
        WC["Weight Calculator\ntext 0.5 / voice 0.3 / face 0.15 / hesit 0.05"]:::fusion
        EA["Emotion Aggregator\nWeighted probability sum"]:::fusion
        CB["Context Builder\nTone selection"]:::fusion
    end

    subgraph RESPONSE["Response"]
        GPT2["GPT-2\nPrompt routing + Sanitization"]:::output
        OUT["Adaptive Reply\ntone + emotion label"]:::output
    end

    T --> BERT
    KS --> HS
    AU --> LBRS
    FR --> CNN

    BERT --> WC
    HS --> WC
    LBRS --> WC
    CNN --> WC

    WC --> EA --> CB --> GPT2 --> OUT
```

