## 4. Typing Behavior and Hesitation Score

```mermaid
flowchart TD
    classDef fe fill:#7B68EE,stroke:#4B3FA0,color:#fff
    classDef compute fill:#16A085,stroke:#0E6655,color:#fff
    classDef score fill:#E67E22,stroke:#784212,color:#fff
    classDef out fill:#27AE60,stroke:#145A32,color:#fff

    subgraph FRONT["Frontend Hook — useTypingBehavior"]
        FO["User focuses input"]:::fe
        KEY["Keystroke event"]:::fe
        REC["recordKeystroke(isDelete)"]:::fe
        PAUSE["Pause detection · interval > 500ms"]:::fe
        META["TypingMetadata\ntyping_duration_ms\npause_intervals_ms\ndelete_count\nkeystroke_count\ncharacter_count"]:::fe
    end

    subgraph BACK["Backend — TypingService"]
        PS["Pause Score\navg_pause / 5000  weight 0.4"]:::compute
        PF["Pause Frequency Score\nweight 0.3"]:::compute
        DS["Delete Score\ndelete / keystrokes / 0.5  weight 0.2"]:::compute
        SS["Speed Score\ninverse chars-per-sec  weight 0.1"]:::compute
        WS["Weighted Sum · clamp 0-1"]:::score
        HS["Hesitation Score 0.0 to 1.0"]:::out
    end

    FO --> KEY --> REC --> PAUSE --> META
    META -->|POST /chat| PS & PF & DS & SS
    PS & PF & DS & SS --> WS --> HS
```

