## 8. Response Generation Pipeline (GPT-2)

```mermaid
flowchart TD
    classDef in fill:#3498DB,stroke:#1A5276,color:#fff
    classDef route fill:#9B59B6,stroke:#5B2C6F,color:#fff
    classDef gen fill:#E67E22,stroke:#784212,color:#fff
    classDef san fill:#27AE60,stroke:#145A32,color:#fff
    classDef val fill:#E74C3C,stroke:#922B21,color:#fff

    CTX2["Fused Context + User Message"]:::in

    subgraph ROUTING["Stage 1 — Prompt Routing"]
        ER{{"Emotion Router"}}:::route
        SAD["SADNESS · empathetic · max 120 tokens"]:::route
        JOY["JOY · warm · max 100 tokens"]:::route
        ANG["ANGER · calm · max 140 tokens"]:::route
        FEA["FEAR · reassuring · max 120 tokens"]:::route
        NEU["NEUTRAL · helpful · max 150 tokens"]:::route
        CON["CONFUSED · clarifying · max 150 tokens"]:::route
    end

    subgraph GEN["Stage 2 — GPT-2 Generation"]
        GPT["GPT2LMHeadModel\ntemp=0.7 · top_p=0.9 · no_repeat_ngram=2"]:::gen
        RAW["Raw output with possible artifacts"]:::gen
    end

    subgraph SAN["Stage 3 — Output Sanitization"]
        S1["Remove 9 stop tokens"]:::san
        S2["Remove 11 contamination patterns\nrole labels · dataset markers · separators"]:::san
        S3["Trim at paragraph break"]:::san
        S4["Enforce sentence boundary"]:::san
        S5["Apply max token limit"]:::san
    end

    subgraph VAL["Stage 4 — Quality Validation"]
        V1{"Length >= 10 chars?"}:::val
        V2{"No contamination markers?"}:::val
        V3{"No incomplete tokens?"}:::val
        FB["Fallback safe response"]:::val
        CLEAN["Clean Response to UI"]:::san
    end

    CTX2 --> ER
    ER --> SAD & JOY & ANG & FEA & NEU & CON
    SAD & JOY & ANG & FEA & NEU & CON --> GPT --> RAW
    RAW --> S1 --> S2 --> S3 --> S4 --> S5
    S5 --> V1 -->|Pass| V2 -->|Pass| V3 -->|Pass| CLEAN
    V1 -->|Fail| FB
    V2 -->|Fail| FB
    V3 -->|Fail| FB
```

