## 10. Privacy Data Flow

```mermaid
flowchart LR
    classDef raw fill:#E74C3C,stroke:#922B21,color:#fff
    classDef feat fill:#27AE60,stroke:#145A32,color:#fff
    classDef store fill:#95A5A6,stroke:#5D7275,color:#fff
    classDef discard fill:#7F8C8D,stroke:#4D5656,color:#fff

    RI["Raw Image Frame"]:::raw --> FE4["Extract face features\nface_rect · region_size"] --> DISC1["Image DISCARDED"]:::discard
    FE4 --> FV1["Face Feature Vector\nJSON only"]:::feat --> FS[(face_features/)]:::store

    RA["Raw Audio WAV"]:::raw --> FE5["Extract speech features\nWPM · pitch · energy · MFCC"] --> DISC2["Audio DISCARDED"]:::discard
    FE5 --> FV2["Speech Feature Vector\nJSON only"]:::feat --> SS2[(speech_features/)]:::store

    RT["Raw Text"]:::raw --> FE6["BERT inference\nemotion probabilities"] --> FV3["Text Feature Vector\nprobabilities · confidence"]:::feat --> TS[(text_features/)]:::store

    KM["Keystroke Metadata\nnot keystrokes content"] --> FE7["Compute hesitation score"] --> FV4["Typing Feature Vector\nhesitation_score · pause_count"]:::feat --> KS2[(typing_features/)]:::store
```

