## 15. Hesitation Score — Weighted Component Breakdown (Bar Chart)

> Decomposition of H for a single high-hesitation message.
> H = 0.4·P_score + 0.3·P_freq + 0.2·D_score + 0.1·Speed_score

```mermaid
xychart-beta
    title "Hesitation Score H — Component Contributions"
    x-axis ["Pause Duration x0.4", "Pause Frequency x0.3", "Delete Ratio x0.2", "Speed Inverse x0.1"]
    y-axis "Weighted Contribution  0.0 → 0.5" 0 --> 0.5
    bar [0.32, 0.21, 0.14, 0.07]
```
